MIME-Version: 1.0

Hi,

Running a Bitcoin node should not require settling for outdated software or=
 a disjointed security setup.

If you are using Bitcoin Core or a similar client, you have likely run into=
 some of its common drawbacks: an aging interface, lack of built-in hardwar=
e wallet support, and manual steps that create extra friction in day-to-day=
 use.

Knots Desktop Client was created to solve those problems.

Knots is a modern, open-source desktop client for Bitcoin nodes and wallets=
, built for users who want complete control without unnecessary complexity.=
 Here is what it offers:

Hardware Wallet Support
Connect your Tangem or Ledger device directly to your node, without third-p=
arty bridge apps or workaround tools.

Multisig Functionality
Spread signing authority across multiple keys for stronger, more flexible s=
ecurity.

Cloud-Enhanced RPC Management
